msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cbackend-development.md:316
msgid "Audit logging spans two files:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cbackend-development.md:318
msgid ""
"`src/types/audit.types.ts` — `AuditLogEntry` interface, the single source of "
"truth for the shape of an audit record"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cbackend-development.md:319
msgid ""
"`src/middleware/audit.middleware.ts` — `auditMiddleware` (automatic per-"
"request logging) and `auditLog()` (explicit action logging from route "
"handlers); re-exports `AuditLogEntry` for backward compatibility"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cbackend-development.md:320
msgid ""
"`src/services/audit.service.ts` — pg-promise connection pool and "
"`persistAuditLog()`"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cbackend-development.md:322
msgid "Automatic vs. explicit logging"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cbackend-development.md:324
msgid ""
"Every authenticated request is logged automatically by `auditMiddleware`, "
"which wraps `res.end` and calls `createAuditLog()` after the response is "
"sent. The action is `${req.method} ${req.path}` and the result is derived "
"from the HTTP status code:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cbackend-development.md:326
msgid "Status range"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cbackend-development.md:326
msgid "Result"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cbackend-development.md:326
msgid "200–399"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cbackend-development.md:326
msgid "`success`"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cbackend-development.md:326
msgid "400–499"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cbackend-development.md:326
msgid "`failure`"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cbackend-development.md:326
msgid "500+"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cbackend-development.md:326
msgid "`error`"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cbackend-development.md:332
msgid ""
"Route handlers can additionally call `auditLog()` directly to record domain-"
"level actions with richer detail:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cbackend-development.md:333
msgid ""
"auditLog(req, 'process.start.zorgtoeslag', 'success', {\n"
"  processInstanceId: instance.id,\n"
"});"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cbackend-development.md:339
msgid "Database persistence"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cbackend-development.md:341
msgid ""
"`persistAuditLog()` in `audit.service.ts` writes each entry to the "
"`audit_logs` table on Azure PostgreSQL Flexible Server using a pg-promise "
"named-parameter `INSERT`. It is called fire-and-forget from `createAuditLog()"
"` — errors are caught and logged but never propagated to the request cycle, "
"so a database outage does not affect API availability."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cbackend-development.md:343
msgid ""
"`initDb()` is called at server startup to verify connectivity. If the "
"database is unreachable at startup, the backend falls back to in-memory "
"logging and logs a warning. In-memory entries are not persisted to the "
"database later; they exist only for the lifetime of the process."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cbackend-development.md:345
msgid ""
"See [PostgreSQL Deployment]{1} for schema, firewall, and connection string "
"setup."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cbackend-development.md:347
msgid "Skipping self-referential entries"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cbackend-development.md:349
msgid ""
"`GET /audit` requests are excluded from the audit log to prevent the Audit "
"Log viewer from recording its own page loads. The skip is applied inside "
"`auditMiddleware` before `createAuditLog()` is called:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cbackend-development.md:350
msgid ""
"if (req.path === '/audit') {\n"
"  return originalEnd.apply(this, args as any);\n"
"}"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cbackend-development.md:356
msgid "Known issues fixed"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cbackend-development.md:358
msgid "**IP address format on Azure App Service**"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cbackend-development.md:360
msgid ""
"`req.ip` on Azure App Service includes the port (`77.161.155.118:40796`). "
"PostgreSQL's `inet` type does not accept a port suffix, causing every "
"`INSERT` to fail silently. Fixed in `audit.service.ts` by stripping the port "
"before the insert:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cbackend-development.md:361
msgid ""
"ipAddress: entry.ipAddress ? entry.ipAddress.replace(/:\\d+$/, '') : null,"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cbackend-development.md:365
msgid "This only affects Azure — local Express sets `req.ip` without a port."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cbackend-development.md:367
msgid "**Audit log viewer pagination reset**"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cbackend-development.md:369
msgid ""
"The `useEffect` that triggers `loadAuditLogs(0)` on section entry "
"incorrectly included `auditLogs.length` in its dependency array. When \"Meer "
"laden\" appended records, the length change re-fired the effect and reset "
"pagination to offset 0. Fixed by removing `auditLogs.length` from the "
"dependency array — `activeSection` changing to `audit-overzicht` or `audit-"
"details` is sufficient to trigger the initial load."
msgstr ""
